string_data: The image shows three women in orange high-visibility vests protesting outside a building with ornate stonework that has been splattered with orange liquid. One protester holds a sign reading "Solidarity with Climate Prisoners," another holds a photo labeled "ANNA HOLLAND" with "IMPRISONED FOR 1 Year 8months," and a third sign reads "Shame on UK Government." A police officer in dark uniform stands nearby observing the demonstration.
